First fy_map. Its on our server (Tango Delta Clan: Public Server) 8.9.3.196:27015.    OVERVIEW

Overview: Made by: -=(TD)=- Drz. Rootbeerz... THIS MAP IS RESTRICED FOR ANY
CHANGES OR EXTENSIONS IF YOU DO NOT ASK ME FIRST.
EMAIL: mattsplace@sbcglobal.net WEBSITE: www.tangodelta.org

Counter-Terrorist: Pretend this is a game of paintball, but you have
only one life. Don't waste it, and take tactics to eliminate the
opposing team. Stay in groups, and plan your attack carefully.
You should come out with a victory.

Terrorist: Eliminate the opposing team, and you shall go on to
be the most recognized paintballer team in the world. Watch your backs
and make sure you don't get caught up in the middle of a firefight.
Use smoke grenades to cover yourself while moving.

Tips and Advice: Take the water level (level 1) to get around to
the other side quicker. Shoot people you see above the grates, and
smoke areas that are needed. Have half of your people stay back,
and the other half rush spread out. Make sure you have all corners
covered, and this shall be an easy victory.

-=(TD)=- Drz. Rootbeerz restricted map, Tango Delta©®
